node.text:
GIVEAWAY!!! I teamed up with @whitefoxboutique to give four of you besties $250 vouchers!! If you want to spoil yourself check below how to enter 🥰🥰🥰 #ad

How to enter:
 1  Follow @whitefoxboutique and @daisymarquez_ 
  2  Tag 2 friends in the comments below
  3  Share this post to your story and tag @whitefoxboutique + @daisymarquez_ for an extra entry
Giveaway I.G Terms
Giveaway open worldwide, winner will be chosen and announced on the @whitefoxboutique account on September 1st AEST
Per Instagram rules, this is in no way sponsored, administered, or associated with Instagram, Inc.

By entering, entrants confirm they are 16+ years of age, release Instagram of responsibility, and agree to Instagram's terms of use.
